data.title: Manifesto checker: What are the Labour, Conservatives', Reform UK's, Liberal Democrats', SNP's, Greens' and Plaid Cymru's key pledges?
data.meta_description: Sky News is scouring the parties' manifestos as they are released - so you do not have to.
data.text:
Labour, the Conservatives, Reform UK, the Liberal Democrats, the Greens, the SNP and Plaid Cymru have released their manifestos - as the general election campaign carries on.

Sky News has scoured their policy pledges so you don't have to. We will add a breakdown of all the other parties' manifestos here when they are announced.

Follow live general election updates

Scroll to the right in the interactive tool below to find out what the parties have promised to do if they win the election on 4 July.
